ConversionObligationContext is a Form
    Layout
        three column
            column1
                RunGroup
                Company
                    select is Companies
            column2
                Customer
                    select is CustomerContextCompanyCustomerSelectList
                InterfacedCustomer
                    label is "ExternalCustomer"
                paragraph
                    ConversionInvoiceType
                        label is "TransactionType"
                    Invoice
                        label is "Transaction"
            column3
                visible when (ErrorExists)
                    ErrorMessage
                        display as text
        blank line
